Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dh-sequence-python3, flit, pybuild-plugin-pyproject, python3-all, python3-doc <!nodoc>, python3-docutils, python3-mistune, python3-pygments, python3-pytest <!nocheck>, python3-sphinx
Description: Sphinx extension for including or writing pages in Markdown This is a Sphinx extension that enables including Markdown documents from within reStructuredText. It provides the `.. mdinclude::` directive, to automatically convert the content of Markdown documents to reStructuredText format.
Package-List: python-sphinx-mdinclude-doc deb doc optional arch=all profile=!nodoc python3-sphinx-mdinclude deb python optional arch=all
